      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DR. BENEDICT (1) is racing well without winning, recording three minors on end, the latest hitting the ground running with a fast early sectional but finishing in the minors again when third (22.84) over 400m at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from three starts. Can measure up this time. MYALL MATE (5) is a promising type who notched his 22nd career success when too good (24.50) at Sale last time. Strike rate this course strong having won three of five tries. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Should feature again. BLAME SPENCER (2) was an impressive winner last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by 2.75 lengths (16.86) at Healesville. Expected to feature again. DR. HAROLD (3) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
